{"tid":1485821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想同大家檢討下一啲運動嘅原則","createTime":"2019-08-18T16:47:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T16:56:30.000Z","uid":16086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"918a7a5fb1022f6e6d2337e87ea1636ab265242b","tid":1485821,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:47:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">我口才廢，有咩講得唔啱大家指點下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n每個人，都有<span style=\"color: orange;\">一個大台</span>，就係<span style=\"color: orange;\">你自己</span><br />\n你自己想點做，想做咩，只要<span style=\"color: orange;\">跟隨自己</span>嘅諗法<br />\n所以，大家都<span style=\"color: red;\">唔應該強迫人</span>跟你嘅「大台」<br />\n你<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">可以提供意見，可以勸告，可以商量</span></span><br />\n但係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">絶對唔可以屌，話手足係鬼嘅更為過份</span></span><br />\n但我都希望所有人，唔理前線定後方<br />\n都時時能夠企喺對方嘅位置思考<br />\n學習<span style=\"color: orange;\">了解對方<br />\n再作決定</span><br />\n而決定<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">以運動為中心</span></span><br />\n一切為 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">光復香港</span></span> 為 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求</span></span><br />\n我地係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">手足</span></span>，我地係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">同一嘅方向</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">尊重</span></span>每一位手足嘅決定<br />\n萬一真係有咩意外，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不割蓆</span></span><br />\n大家再<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">一齊諗辦法拆掂佢</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你真係好不滿，要同對方檢查<br />\n唔緊要嘅，因為大家個初心都係想個運動好<br />\n但係我認為有個原則<br />\n就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對外嘅槍口一定要比對內嘅多</span></span><br />\n記住，對付敵人⼀定係首要<br />\n<br />\n而對於今日嘅行動，我覺得有位手足講得好好<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">後排要有上前的勇氣</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">前線也要有退後的胸襟</span></span><br />\n<br />\n前後雙方，本是同根"},{"pid":"a39e8e66540e78e996ad81ca13ec2e336d55dceb","tid":1485821,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:48:01.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"ee488592654df6f87b6c430ccfce834d4c16f761","tid":1485821,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:49:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/flyingshadows/videos/2412061705701511\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fflyingshadows%2Fvideos%2F2412061705701511&d=T%2BmtXVGNOTzTHFJD9Tq3cYleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=5b0b9824\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/flyingshadows/videos/2412061705701511</a><br />\n\t<br />\n扮示威者收工返警總</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n記得有巴打講過紅土遊行之後有班示威者行到旺角警署出面，有一個鬼不斷叫在場人士留低，又不斷話「點解要走呀？」之類嘅說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但明明當日冇計劃過任何嘅圍堵行動，我相信宜家金鐘都係一樣情況，都係有班鬼不斷叫人唔好走，宜家共識都係叫走，到呢一刻喺現場仲叫留低嘅人好大機會係鬼<br />\n<br />\n我可能無能力勸到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我只係希望大家可以智勇雙全，理性啲講，宜家仲keep住要留低嘅仲有啲乜嘢目標？我剩係知道今日嘅戰略目標（搶佔國際輿論）已經超標完成，到呢一刻仲要留低對成個運動仲有乜嘢positive effect ？定係比黑警打一身之後仲要聽日報紙頭版就係衝突畫面？求下你地，大家一齊走，好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後話：<br />\n<br />\n今日總結，我認為大家要互相體諒，畢竟大家都冇上帝視角，有各自嘅限制<br />\n<br />\n例如之前呢三個鐘已經去到金鐘同散咗場嘅巴打，因為擔心前線安危，加上今日目標已經達成，冇必要死守，所以叫走，但始終人已經唔係身處現場，冇上帝視角，望住live 仲見到咁多人，自然開始心急，語氣上亦變得唔係太好<br />\n<br />\n同時之間，前線亦想所有人平平安安走曬，自己最後一批先走，咁當然一定會有鬼從中叫人留低/ 賴死唔走，迫你留低「保護」佢哋，同樣前線亦冇上帝視角，難以判斷係手足定係鬼，散嘅速度自然亦會慢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都係呢一句：<br />\n永不割蓆，永不分化，保持改進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01de312693612593dc413c378f78856e6deba7a5","tid":1485821,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:53:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b048e08a204c52f2079ec9051367e07539e53c0","tid":1485821,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:53:33.000Z","msg":"個人感想，其實今日我見到有人留守，<br />\n係真心有啲嬲，好想屌人！<br />\n但係諗到大家都係手足，<br />\n就知要冷一冷靜，唔應該屌，<br />\n頂多講多兩句勸下"},{"pid":"bbb53d6970761fee22a2844ca7b0949d06714234","tid":1485821,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:53:58.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"bba5f4f7fc1ba1de24c072cee3263aa63bc9d3d7","tid":1485821,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:54:08.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"5812855a78ae7ec91c40043fffea8c5edd6d3baa","tid":1485821,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:54:24.000Z","msg":"自推3<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389ef393379628afacc27e5f21af44108c2d57e1","tid":1485821,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:54:40.000Z","msg":"自推4<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21e3eb0012dabb7c4defa233ec0efe7591a519b","tid":1485821,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:54:55.000Z","msg":"自推5<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28dac1cb8344d49c947ffbff9a3069e358540fd6","tid":1485821,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:55:12.000Z","msg":"自推6<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c512f103ef9028c9fee04aaa6f96c00f8072acd","tid":1485821,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:55:26.000Z","msg":"自推7<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c12d517529f2f0d8d684ebbc274b5adc17b278","tid":1485821,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:55:38.000Z","msg":"自推8<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9a8a282ad2f01539a56c8ca9651a83c5059488d","tid":1485821,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:55:52.000Z","msg":"自推9<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc7b5143014305fa694fcc3b774bdaa126a7fc6","tid":1485821,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:56:08.000Z","msg":"自推10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a9599ccff10aaef92bab95e58ee20b54d1bdb6","tid":1485821,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:56:30.000Z","msg":"大家早啲休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}